---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const { locale, dir, t } = Astro.locals;
const updated = "June 29, 2026";
---

<Layout locale={locale} dir={dir} t={t}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-foreground/80">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm text-[#E8A840] hover:text-[#F5D06A] transition-colors">&larr; Back to NoorJyoti</a>
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl text-[#F5D06A] mt-8 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-foreground/50 mb-10">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 leading-relaxed">
      <p>NoorJyoti ("NoorJyoti", "we", "us") is a free service that reads public-domain
      scriptures aloud in AI voices. We care about your privacy and collect as little
      data as possible. This policy explains what we collect, why, and your choices.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Information we collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Account information</strong> — if you choose to create an account, our
        authentication provider collects your email address and name so we can save your
        preferences and listening history. You can use much of NoorJyoti without an account.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — aggregate, non-identifying analytics (e.g. which
        scriptures are played, pages visited, language chosen) to improve the service.</li>
        <li><strong>Local preferences</strong> — your chosen language and settings are stored
        on your own device (local storage), not on our servers.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect health information, we do <strong>not</strong> build
      advertising profiles from your religious or scripture choices, and we do
      <strong>not</strong> sell your personal data to anyone.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">How we use information</h2>
      <p>To provide and improve NoorJyoti: to deliver audio, remember your preferences, keep the
      service secure and reliable, and understand which content people find meaningful.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Service providers</h2>
      <p>We rely on trusted providers who process data only to run NoorJyoti — including
      authentication, cloud hosting/CDN, and audio storage. Each is bound by its own privacy
      and security commitments and may process data outside your country.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Your rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on where you live (including the EU/UK under GDPR and California under CCPA),
      you may have the right to access, correct, export, or delete your personal data, and to
      object to certain processing. To exercise any of these, email
      <a href="mailto:hello@noorjyoti.app" class="text-[#E8A840] hover:text-[#F5D06A]">hello@noorjyoti.app</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Children</h2>
      <p>NoorJyoti is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal
      information from them.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Changes</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We will revise the "last updated" date above
      and, for material changes, provide a more prominent notice.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-[#E8A840] pt-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@noorjyoti.app" class="text-[#E8A840] hover:text-[#F5D06A]">hello@noorjyoti.app</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
